# MarketMind — Full Stack Setup

## File Structure
```
marketmind-backend/
  server.js              ← Node.js backend (zero npm dependencies)
  start.js               ← Entry point (loads .env then starts server)
  .env.example           ← Copy to .env and fill in your API key
  db/
    marketmind.json      ← Auto-created user database
  marketmind-login.html  ← Login / Register page
  marketmind-main.html   ← Main app (connects to backend)
```

## Quick Start

### 1. Add your Anthropic API key
```bash
cp .env.example .env
# Open .env and set:
#   ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...your-key...
```

### 2. Start the backend server
```bash
node start.js
```
You'll see:
```
╔══════════════════════════════════════════╗
║   MarketMind Backend  — port 3001        ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════╝
  Anthropic key: ✓ set
```

### 3. Open the app
Open `marketmind-main.html` in your browser (double-click or use a local server).

Use `Live Server` in VS Code or:
```bash
npx serve .
# or
python3 -m http.server 5500
```

Then visit: http://localhost:5500/marketmind-main.html

---

## API Endpoints

| Method | Route | Auth | Description |
|--------|-------|------|-------------|
| GET  | `/api/health` | — | Server health check |
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | — | Create account |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | — | Sign in, returns JWT |
| POST | `/api/auth/logout` | JWT | Revoke token |
| GET  | `/api/auth/me` | JWT | Get current user |
| POST | `/api/ai/strategy` | JWT | Generate AI strategy |
| POST | `/api/ai/chat` | JWT | Ask AI a question |

---

## Authentication Flow

```
User fills login form
       ↓
POST /api/auth/login
       ↓
Server verifies password (HMAC-SHA256)
       ↓
Returns JWT token
       ↓
Frontend stores token in localStorage
       ↓
All AI requests include: Authorization: Bearer <token>
       ↓
Server verifies JWT + calls Anthropic (API key stays server-side)
```

---

## Security Features
- Passwords hashed with HMAC-SHA256 + random salt (never stored plain)
- JWT signed with HS256, 24-hour expiry
- Token blacklist on logout (persisted to disk)
- Rate limiting: 10 auth attempts / minute per IP, 20 AI calls / minute per user
- Anthropic API key never exposed to frontend
- CORS restricted to configured origins

---

## Requirements
- Node.js 16+ (built-in modules only — no npm install needed)
- An Anthropic API key from console.anthropic.com